### Incidents
GET http://localhost:5090/support/incidents

### Alerts
GET http://localhost:5090/support/alerts

### Knowledge base
GET http://localhost:5090/support/knowledge

### Update incident status
PUT http://localhost:5090/support/incidents/{{incidentId}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": "Resolved",
  "owner": "Ayşe"
}

### Add incident action
POST http://localhost:5090/support/incidents/{{incidentId}}/actions
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "actionType": "note",
  "actor": "console",
  "notes": "Mitigation steps confirmed"
}
